{"tid":608410,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[高登仔又發功] 「你個嘢壞咗呀」變真●有聲post，未夠2日就已經有4萬點擊率！","createTime":"2018-03-28T06:31:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-30T16:45:52.000Z","uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"982d98a3b242b74da9a959ff79f9b16ac658b7b5","tid":608410,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T06:31:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6880631&amp;page=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D6880631%26page%3D1&d=hkTZ7ysebLic5YBkGO%2FL2Bv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=f1851fbf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6880631&amp;page=1</a><br />\n<br />\n今時今日高登仲可以上報紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180326/large/1522079578_445a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180326%2Flarge%2F1522079578_445a.png&h=61cefeb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2014年年底一次冬日美食節，一位熱衷玩遊戲夾龍蝦嘅女士，憑藉一句「你個嘢壞咗呀」紅遍網絡，網民淨係見到呢幾隻字，個腦都不自覺浮咗把聲出嚟。原本以為「龍蝦姐」從此絕跡江湖，誰不知舊年暑假嘅美食博覽，龍蝦姐忽然驚喜現身排足3日2夜通宵，再次出戰拋福袋大賽，又試捧走人哋18個鮑魚福袋。<br />\n<br />\n為咗歌頌呢位識飲識食又識玩嘅老友記，高登仔發功重新填詞，將「你個嘢壞咗呀」呢句洗腦台詞，完美嵌入譚校長名曲「霧之戀」，配上《蘋果動新聞》當年直擊片段，成功令「龍蝦姐」同疑似譚校長合唱一曲，令個post變咗「真●有聲」，堪稱經典。有幾好笑？我唔直接答你，我用條片嚟答你，去片！<br />\n<br />\n順帶一提，其實「龍蝦姐」王女士舊年喺美食博覽大方接受訪問，都提到自從2014年「霸氣外露」之後，每年冬夏兩季美食展都被網民取笑，好苦惱，排隊時仲聽到有人講佢，希望大家手下留情咁話。龍蝦姐放心啦，江山代有才人出，話唔定今年美食博覽就有人接班呢！<br />\n<br />\n龍蝦姐出戰2014年冬日美食節「個嘢壞咗」實錄經典重溫：<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2GtlS4g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2GtlS4g&d=hkTZ7ysebLic5YBkGO%2FL2Bv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=05262630\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2GtlS4g</a><br />\n<br />\n龍蝦姐2017年美食博覽重出江湖拋福袋：<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2upUsqS\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2upUsqS&d=hkTZ7ysebLic5YBkGO%2FL2Bv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=af2905dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2upUsqS</a><br />\n<br />\n高登音樂台足本播放：<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Ge0igE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Ge0igE&d=hkTZ7ysebLic5YBkGO%2FL2Bv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=84c6e12b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Ge0igE</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180328/57999048\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180328%2F57999048&d=hkTZ7ysebLic5YBkGO%2FL2Bv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=a0c550cd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180328%2F57999048&h=9e7d4ac3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180328/57999048</a>"},{"pid":"c74542cc2f932a08a86c3ca692ea5ab964e2b1b6","tid":608410,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T06:40:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>網民回應</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\nwinccc:<br />\n高登音樂真係成個forum嘅清泉<img src=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/faces/lomore/agree.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Ffaces%2Flomore%2Fagree.gif&h=5a3ae2a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n躺著也中槍!:<br />\n高登校長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n特首曾蔭權:<br />\n龍蝦姐真係陰公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咖喱卷:<br />\n其實阿姐應該自豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1382954c8ed1ec54f172f43c7336e59e25621d57","tid":608410,"uid":20914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T16:45:52.000Z","msg":"成件事好有回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoj